title: Bengal Sweets Centre and The Pantry Pure Veg Restaurant
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, International, Fast food, Take-out
description: A grand counter filled with display of savory sweets and assorted snack mixes greets you as you enter. Well-lit, clean, modern, casual kind of place. Seats in the back of the room. Must have a samosas. Fast, friendly service. Good food. Confirmed open Jan 2010.
